@M_KOJO_SUCCESS_COM_K142_300
;成否判定
;TFLAG:192(-2=コマンド終了、-1＝強制失敗、0=COM依存、1=強制成功or大成功
TFLAG:192 =0

@M_KOJO_MESSAGE_COM_K142_300
;コマンド共通メッセージ(TRAIN_MESSAGE) 
;削除すると「～話をした。」とかが消えます。また、削除した場合は自動で口上色が付きません。
;口上メイン呼出
CALL M_KOJO_MESSAGE_COM_K142_300_1
RETURN RESULT

@M_KOJO_MESSAGE_COM_K142_300_1
;-------------------------------------------------
;記入チェック（=0, 非表示、1, 表示）
LOCAL = 1
;-------------------------------------------------
IF LOCAL
	IF CHK_DATENOW(CFLAG:TARGET:デート中)

		SELECTCASE RAND:2
			CASE 0
				SELECTCASE CFLAG:MASTER:現在位置 / 100

					CASE 0 ;Hakurei Shrine
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「Hey, %CALLNAME:MASTER%... you got any cash on ya?」
								PRINTFORMW 「I wanna donate to the shrine before we go.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I don't ask the gods for favors, but I wanna stay on their good sides. Especially the one that the Hakurei Shrine Maiden worships.」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「They say there's some kinda ship from the future near the shrine.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Crazy, huh? I wonder what they came to Gensokyo for...」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORMW 「So does Hakurei adopt everyone %HE_SHE(1)% beats in a fight, or...?」
								PRINTFORML 「First that oni moved in after %HE_SHE(1)% beat %HIM_HER(10)%. Then the inchling, then the hell fairy, then the dog...」
								PRINTFORMW 「How does %HE_SHE(1)% manage to keep 'em all fed? I though %HE_SHE(1)% was broke!」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 1 ;Myouren Temple
						SELECTCASE RAND:4
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「One time I stopped by here because I heard Hijiri was givin' out free food after the sermon.」
								PRINTFORMW 「But %HE_SHE(55)% didn't tell us it was all vegetarian crap!」
								PRINTFORMDW Momoyo scowls.
								PRINTFORMW 「That's three hours of my life I'm never gettin' back...」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「I don't usually come down here.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Sometimes I stop by after a Choujuu Gigaku concert, but that's about it.」
								PRINTFORMW 「So what's there to see? They got any cool lookin' rocks?」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「Iizunamaru says %HE_SHE(140)% supports Hijiri's ideology, because it means more humans'll be willin' to trade with us.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Y'think they'll let us mine on their turf, too? I bet there's all kinds'a cool stuff buried there!」

							CASE 3
								PRINTFORML 「That Tatara %PRINT_MALE("guy", 40)%'s one heck of a blacksmith.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I usually have %HIM_HER(40)% repair my tools when they get damaged. %HIS_HER(40,1)% prices are way cheaper than the kappa's.」
								PRINTFORMW 「It's crazy. %HES_SHES(40,1)% been able to smelt everything I've asked her to!」
								PRINTFORMW 「I remember tellin' %HIM_HER(40)% how surprised I was, and %HE_SHE(40)% just started beamin' at me.」
								PRINTFORML 「If you find any cool ores in our mine, you should take it to %HIM_HER(40)% and see what %HE_SHE(40)% can do with 'em.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I bet %HE_SHE(40)%'ll surprise you, too!」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 2 ;Human Village
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORMW 「I hear a lotta youkai visit here undercover.」
								PRINTFORML 「Shameimaru's always lookin' for a new scoop, Futatsuiwa's tryin' to increase the tanuki's influence...」
								CALL PRINT_STRW, @"「Heck, there could be a youkai standin' next to ya @ITALIC@right now@!」"
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% snickers.

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「Apparently tengu come down here in disguise to look for human lovers.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% scowls.
								PRINTFORMW 「Not that I'm worried about that. I'm way cuter'n any of them!」
								PRINTFORMDW %BREAKENG(@"Despite her words, you notice %HES_SHES([[百々世]])% fiddling with %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% hair and clothes when %HE_SHE([[百々世]])% thinks you aren't looking.")%

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「Hey, next time you come down here... make sure to tell everyone how scary oomukade are, OK?」
								PRINTFORMW 「I don't think the humans are takin' us seriously. I'm not smellin' any fear on 'em at all!」
								PRINTFORMDW Does %HE_SHE([[百々世]])% think humans normally live in constant terror of youkai all the time?
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 3 ;Scarlet Devil Mansion
						SELECTCASE RAND:5
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「I hear that when this mansion showed up, the %PRINT_MALE("guy", 16)% in charge went on a rampage.」
								PRINTFORMW 「After %HE_SHE(16)% got beat, Hakurei set up the spell card rules.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I guess I owe %HIM_HER(16)% one, huh? It was way harder to find sparring partners before then.」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「So the %PRINT_MALE("guy", 16)% in charge of this place is a vampire, yeah?」
								PRINTFORMW 「Does %HE_SHE(16)% drink %HIS_HER(16)% employees' blood? 'Cause the %PRINT_MALE("guy", 58)% at the gate reeks of dragon.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Wonder what %HIS_HER(58)% blood tastes like...」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「Knowledge calls %HIMSELF_HERSELF(54)% the Seven-Day Magician, right?」
								PRINTFORMW 「And Margatroid in the forest calls %HIMSELF_HERSELF(17)% the Seven-Colored Puppeteer.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Guess the number seven is a big deal to magicians, huh?」
								PRINTFORMW 「Maybe I should start calling myself the "Can Curl Around You Seven and a Half Times Oomukade?"」
								PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% chuckles.
								PRINTFORMW 「Nah, that's way too long. And way too pretentious.」

							CASE 3
								PRINTFORMW 「That ice fairy keeps on challengin' me to Danmaku matches.」
								PRINTFORML 「I've always turned %HIM_HER(14)% down. There's no honor in fightin' somebody weaker than you.」
								PRINTFORMW 「But %HE_SHE(TARGET)% just won't take no for an answer.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Hell, the other day %HE_SHE(14)% told me %HE_SHE(14)% won a match against Matara back when the seasons were all screwed up.」
								PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% rolls %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% eyes.
								PRINTFORMW 「C'mon... If you're gonna lie, at least make it believable.」

							CASE 4
								PRINTFORML 「That Wakasagihime %PRINT_MALE("guy", TARGET)% lives in the lake, right?」
								PRINTFORMW 「Y'think %HES_SHES(93)% a princess, too? Or is "Hime" just %HIS_HER(93)% personal name?」
								PRINTFORMW 「Maybe I should ask if we run into %HIM_HER(93)%.」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 4 ;Bamboo Forest of the Lost
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「I hear that scumbag Fujiwara lives around here.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% smiles grimly.
								PRINTFORMW 「If we meet %HIM_HER(61)%... do me a favor and look away. You really don't wanna see what I'm gonna do to %HIM_HER(61)%.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Y'see, %HE_SHE(61)% killed someone very important to me. And I'm gonna make that %PRINT_MALE("bastard:bitch", 61)% pay for it.」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「%CHAN_KUN([[リグル]])%'s friend Kazami lives around here, doesn't %HE_SHE(68)%?」
								PRINTFORMW 「%HE_SHE(68,1)% might not look like it, but %HES_SHES(68)% actually one of the strongest people in Gensokyo.」
								PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grimaces.
								PRINTFORMW 「I've racked up a pretty embarrassing losing streak against %HIM_HER(68)%...」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「The nice thing about bein' an oomukade is that we never get lost.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Sometimes we ain't sure where everything else is... but we always know exactly where we are.」
								PRINTFORML 「And if that happens, you just pick a direction...」
								PRINTFORMW 「And start diggin' through everything in your way until you find whatever it is you're lookin' for!」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 5 ;Forest of Magic
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「That witch %PRINT_MALE("guy", 11)% lives around here, right?」
								PRINTFORMW 「The one who steals from everyone?」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% scowls.
								PRINTFORML 「If you want somebody's stuff, you challenge 'em to a fight and put up something of equal value as your stake.」
								PRINTFORMW 「That's how it oughta be.」
								PRINTFORMW 「What kinda place would Gensokyo be if everyone stole from each other?」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「Oh hey, this is %CHAN_KUN([[リグル]])%'s home!」
								PRINTFORMW 「We go way back. At least three years!」
								PRINTFORML 「%HES_SHES([[リグル]],1)% lots of fun... but I wish %HE_SHE([[リグル]])%'d talk about somethin' other than bugs once in a while.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I mean, yeah, I know she thinks they're super cool and all, but you gotta realize that not everyone does.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% sighs.
								PRINTFORML 「I remember one time %HE_SHE([[リグル]])% found a huge piece'a stone streaked through with tektites, and all %HE_SHE([[リグル]])% cared about were the bugs under it!」
								PRINTFORMW 「I'd never seen a piece that big, either...」
								PRINTFORMDW You tune %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% out as %HE_SHE([[百々世]])% keeps rambling about minerals.

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「Sometimes %CHAN_KUN([[リグル]])% and I check out Kourindou to see if there's anything cool there.」
								PRINTFORMW 「One time I found a chunk of hihi'irokane in there... but when I took it to the counter, Morichika told me it was reserved for Kirisame.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Somethin' about "Mini-Hakkero repairs".」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% frowns.
								PRINTFORML 「C'mon, %HE_SHE(11)% can't need that whole thing, can %HE_SHE(11)%?」
								PRINTFORMW 「I'd be able to get so much more mining done if I could make a pickaxe head outta it...」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 6 ;Sanzu River～Netherworld
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「Man... it's kinda surreal bein' able to see the afterlife from here.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% stares out over the Sanzu River.
								PRINTFORMW (I wonder if that shinigami was the one who took my mom across all those centuries ago?)

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORMW 「You smell that?」
								PRINTFORMDW You sniff the air. You don't smell anything.
								PRINTFORML 「Exactly.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% scowls.
								PRINTFORMW 「I haven't been able to smell a damn thing except you since we got here.」
								PRINTFORMW 「And oomukade navigate by smell! It's like if you went somewhere where there was no sound at all!」
								PRINTFORMDW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% glances at you.
								PRINTFORML 「I'm no coward... but I'm not gonna lie, this place gives me the creeps.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Can we go somewhere else?」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「I don't like this place... but I can't help but wonder what kinda minerals they have here.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Wasn't there a whole thing where Old Hell had this huge oil well that everyone forgot about?」
								PRINTFORMW 「Y'think vengeful spirits can turn into ore, too?」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 7 ;Youkai Mountain (Foot)
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML %BREAKENG(@"「Iizunamaru told us that the amanojackass is trying to get %HIS_HER(97)% hands on Ability Cards, and that we need to tell people here not to sell to %HIM_HER(97)%.」")%
								PRINTFORMW 「I'm not too worried. Who's gonna sell to %HIM_HER(97)%? And you can't take the cards by force, or they'll stop workin'.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Unless %HE_SHE(97)% can reverse that so they only work if you steal 'em...」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% looks a little nervous.

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「I come here every once in a while to see of the kappa have anything cool.」
								PRINTFORMW 「The other day, they had this massive set of titanium hand powered drills.」
								PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% rubs the head of %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% pickaxe.
								PRINTFORML 「I've been through a lot with this ol' girl... but I was thinkin' it was time to retire her.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Unfortunately it was too expensive, and Iizunamaru wouldn't let me write it off as a business expense.」
								PRINTFORMDW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% sighs.
								PRINTFORMW 「One day, though... I'll save up enough cash for 'em.」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「This is where the Akis live, right?」
								PRINTFORMW 「Is %CALLNAME:78% the one with the hat, or is that %CALLNAME:77%? I can never remember...」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 8 ;Youkai Mountain (Summit)
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「Iizunamaru always talks about how beautiful it is up here... but my vision ain't great, so I can't really appreciate it.」
								PRINTFORMW 「It does smell pretty damn nice, though!」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% sniffs the air.
								PRINTFORMW 「Oooh, there's a couple shiretoko violets growin' about five minute's walk from here! You wanna go see 'em?」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「As crazy as it sounds, you can actually walk to Heaven from here.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Well, you could if they actually let people in. They're overcrowded.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% sighs.
								PRINTFORMW 「Damn shame. I bet they've got all kinds'a cool ores to mine up there.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I mean, it wouldn't be Heaven if they didn't!」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「On my days off, I usually get some cardio in by swimmin' around in one of the lakes around here.」
								PRINTFORMW 「You wanna join me sometime? It's great exercise.」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 9 ;Underworld
						SELECTCASE RAND:4
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORMW 「What's the deal with that bridgekeeper?」
								PRINTFORML 「I was heading down here the other day to do a lil' pub crawlin', and I had to give %HIM_HER([[パルスィ]])% my name and reason for comin'..」
								PRINTFORML 「But when I was walkin' off, I got this real... menacing feeling. Like the air behind me was rumbling.」
								PRINTFORMW 「So I turned around... and %HE_SHE([[パルスィ]])% was glarin' at me like I'd spat in %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% face or somethin'..」
								PRINTFORMW 「And %HE_SHE([[パルスィ]])% was gnawin' on %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% thumb and mutterin' somethin' under %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% breath.」
								PRINTFORML 「But the worst part was %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% eyes.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I swear they were glowin' a little.」
								PRINTFORML 「Soon as %HE_SHE([[パルスィ]])% saw I was lookin', %HE_SHE([[百々世]])% stopped and went back to normal.」
								PRINTFORMW 「And then that night, I woke up in the middle of the night with a backache. Felt like someone had been hammerin' nails into it.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grimaces.
								IF TALENT:[[パルスィ]]:恋人
									PRINTFORML 「But now %HES_SHES([[パルスィ]])% totally different!」
									PRINTFORMW 「%HES_SHES([[パルスィ]],1)% just got this dreamy smile on %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% face all the time. And this weird glint in %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% eyes.」
									PRINTFORMW 「Like %HES_SHES([[パルスィ]])% so in love it's almost made %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% go nuts.」
									PRINTFORMW 「Man, %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])% eyes are so beautiful... I'm so jealous.」
									PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% pauses and shakes %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% head.
									PRINTFORMW 「What the heck did I say that for? Anyway...」
								ENDIF
								PRINTFORMW 「%HE_SHE([[パルスィ]],1)% just gives me bad vibes. I dunno what's wrong with %HIS_HER([[パルスィ]])%, but I try to take the geyser route whenever I visit the Underworld.」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「We get all our energy from down here. Well, kind of.」
								PRINTFORMW 「The kappa buy it from the Underworld, and we buy it from them.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Iizunamaru's tryin' to negotiate a deal with Komeiji to buy our energy directly and cut out the middleman.」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「Years and years ago, I had a couple oni friends.」
								PRINTFORMW 「But then they told me that they were all movin' to Hell.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Said they were sick of being scammed by humans and wanted to go somewhere they couldn't get to.」
								PRINTFORML 「The years went by, and eventually I forgot all about 'em.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Then those geysers started poppin' up, and people on the surface started visiting Old Hell.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I decided to check the place out, and I was drinkin' in the tavern when I saw 'em.」
								PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grins.
								PRINTFORMW 「My old buddies were drinking at a nearby table!」
								PRINTFORMW 「I ran over and said hi, and we spent the whole night drinkin' and catchin' up on things.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Maybe you've met 'em? Akane and Aoi. The Kurashiki twins.」
								PRINTFORMW 「The four of us should go out for drinks sometime!」
								PRINTFORMW 「But don't drink anything Akane offers you. she's a die hard prankster. Prolly put wasabi in it or somethin'.」

							CASE 3
								PRINTFORML 「We've been negotiatin' with %CALLNAME:49% Komeiji in order to expand into the Underworld market.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Gotta say, I'm glad I'm not the one doing it.」
								PRINTFORMW 「It's gotta be real tough to try and negotiate with somebody who can read your mind.」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 10 ;Dream World～Moon
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「So, uh... how'd we get here, exactly?」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% looks confused.
								PRINTFORMW 「We walked here, right? But you can't walk to the moon. You need a flyin' machine or a portal or somethin'.」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORML 「So there's a passage to the Dream World here, huh?」
								PRINTFORMW 「Now I'm kinda curious about what you dream about.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Me, maybe～?」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「The people up here are real strong.」
								PRINTFORML 「The Watatsuki sisters, Lapislazuli...」
								PRINTFORMW 「But mark my words, one day I'm gonna beat 'em all!」
								PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grins and flexes.
								PRINTFORMW 「I'm gonna train everyday until I'm the strongest Danmaku fighter in history!」
						ENDSELECT

					CASE 11 ;Makai
						SELECTCASE RAND:3
							CASE 0
								PRINTFORML 「Now that Makai's opened back up, %CALLNAME:102%'s tryin' to drum up tourism again.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I'm guessin' it's mostly gonna be Makai People comin' to Gensokyo proper...」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% gestures at the scenery around %HIM_HER([[百々世]])%.
								PRINTFORMW 「This ain't exactly a great place for vacationing.」
								PRINTFORMW 「It's so humid you can damn near squeeze moisture outta the air, everything reeks of sulfur, and everywhere's either boiling hot or freezing cold.」
								PRINTFORMW 「...Why did we come down here, again?」

							CASE 1
								PRINTFORMW 「That %CALLNAME:102% %PRINT_MALE("guy_:lady", 102)%... %HES_SHES(102)% supposed to be a %PRINT_MALE("god:goddess", 102)%, right?」
								PRINTFORMW 「And %CALLNAME:[[リグル]]% told me that Kazami told %HIM_HER([[リグル]])% that when the two of them fought years and years ago, the battle destroyed Pandemonium.」
								PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grins.
								PRINTFORMW 「I'd love to fight %HIM_HER(102)% in Danmaku...」

							CASE 2
								PRINTFORML 「Ever since Makai opened back up, the kappa've been buyin' loads of plasteel from %CALLNAME:102%.」
								PRINTFORMW 「Apparently it's some kinda super strong metal, and it's way more durable than anything you can get on the surface.」
								PRINTFORMW 「I wonder what other cool stuff they've got buried down here...」
						ENDSELECT
				ENDSELECT
			CASE 1
				GOTO REGULAR_CONVOS
		ENDSELECT
		RETURN 1
	ENDIF

	$REGULAR_CONVOS
	SELECTCASE IFRAND("0, 2TO14", 1, "1", CFLAG:[[百々世]]:K142EN_WORK_HELP_PERMISSION == 0, "15TO30", ABL:[[百々世]]:親密 >= 2, "31", ABL:[[百々世]]:親密 >= 2 && ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力 >= ABL:[[百々世]]:戦闘能力 - 1, "32TO37", TALENT:[[百々世]]:恋人, "38", DAY:2 == 4 && ABL:[[百々世]]:親密 >= 2)
		CASE 0
			PRINTFORML 「Y'know, there's all kinds of superstitions about the mines.」
			PRINTFORMW %BREAKENG(@"「Everything from ghosts of dead miners to cave creatures to eldritch horrors, just waitin' for some idiot to dig too deep and let 'em out.」")%
			PRINTFORMW 「And honestly, there's some truth to 'em. You see some real freaky stuff in my line of work.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Just the other day, I was diggin' a new tunnel... and I coulda sworn I heard a woman screamin' "NO!" at the other end.」
			PRINTFORMW 「But when I ran back there to check... nothin'.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% shivers.
			PRINTFORMW 「At least I've never had to deal with anythin' hostile. Just freaky noises and stuff.」

		CASE 1
			PRINTFORMW 「If you were thinkin' of lookin' for treasure down in the mines... don't.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Not only is it full of yin-yang orbs and stuff shootin' at you, there's no air once you get to the deepest parts.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Unless you got some kinda... I dunno, really long breathing rod?」

		CASE 2
			PRINTFORMW 「Iizunamaru says there's all kinds a'fancy magic stuff buried in the mines.」
			PRINTFORMW 「We're just here for Dragon Gems, though.」

		CASE 3
			PRINTFORMW 「Y'heard about that underground gambling den in the mountains?」
			PRINTFORML 「Apparently they opened a sister location in the Human Village.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Human gamblers kept tryin' to go to the other one and they didn't want to risk potential customers gettin' hurt.」
