			PRINTFORMW 「I've had her head replaced, right? But I've also had her handle replaced.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I don't think there's a single piece of her that hasn't been replaced.」
			PRINTFORMW 「So... is it the same pickaxe I bought all those years ago?」
			PRINTFORMW 「And if you really want your mind blown... what if I found all the pieces I replaced and made a pickaxe out of 'em?」
			PRINTFORMW 「Which pickaxe would be my pickaxe? This one? The one I just made? Both? Neither?」
			PRINTFORMDW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% chuckles.
