		CASE 5
			PRINTFORMW 「Feels like everyone's schemin' something these days.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Tenkyuu and Iizunamaru are tryin' to come up with something new now that they reconciled...」
			PRINTFORMW 「The Moriyas are always up to something...」
			PRINTFORMW 「Kudamaki's always up to no good...」
			PRINTFORMW 「Hell, even Tamatsukuri's probably schemin'. Wasn't %HE_SHE(138)% the one who sicced that witch on me a couple years back?」
			PRINTFORMW 「And then there's me.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grins.
			PRINTFORMW 「I just wanna dig holes.」

		CASE 6
			PRINTFORMW 「You learn to trust your gut pretty quick in the mines.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I remember one time, I broke though this wall and ended up in a tunnel.」
			PRINTFORMW 「But everything about it put me on edge. The air smelled bad, the tunnel looked like it'd been gnawed, not dug...」
			PRINTFORMW 「And I swear I saw this creepy purple altar-lookin' thing at the end. Just sittin' there, glowing.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I got the hell out of there, sealed off that section of the mines, and marked it on our maps as "DO NOT DIG".」
			PRINTFORMW 「I'm no coward, but there's brave and then there's reckless.」

		CASE 7
			PRINTFORMW 「I wanna upgrade to a more powerful pickaxe one of these days. Maybe diamond, or chlorophyte.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% sighs.
			PRINTFORMW 「Unfortunately, we gotta pay for all our own equipment. Iizunamaru says that Tenma barely gives us a budget.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Which is weird, because we're always makin' loads of money, and Iizunamaru's always wearin' new fancy outfits...」
			PRINTFORMW 「But I'm a miner, not an accountant. I'm sure there's a good reason for it.」

		CASE 8
			PRINTFORML 「Why do I always carry a pickaxe and shovel around?」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grins.
			PRINTFORMW 「Y'never know when you'll see somethin' you wanna dig up! It happens more often than you'd think.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Or maybe you wanna put down some minecart tracks, but theres's a mountain in the way.」
			PRINTFORMW 「There's all kinds of reasons to carry 'em around! "Always be prepared", that's my motto!」

		CASE 9
			GOTO REGULAR_CONVOS

		CASE 10
			PRINTFORMW 「I wouldn't put too much trust in the tengu newspapers if I were you.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Most of 'em will just make up stuff if they think it'll sell more than the truth.」
			PRINTFORMW 「That doesn't mean you shouldn't buy 'em, though. The coupons are worth every yen!」
			PRINTFORMW 「Well, except for the ones that're half off subscriptions to the same paper...」

		CASE 11
			PRINTFORML 「You play soccer at all, %CALLNAME:MASTER%? We've got a team up here, and we're pretty damn good.」
			PRINTFORMW 「'Course, we play Gensokyo style, so there might be more bullets flyin' around than you're used to.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I'm surprised the balls don't disintegrate on us. Dunno what Tamatsukuri makes 'em out of, but it's damn durable.」

		CASE 12
			PRINTFORMW 「Just a heads up. If you're visitin' Youkai Mountain, well... most tengu don't really like outsiders.」
			PRINTFORMW 「None of the best Youkai Mountain restaurants will let you in unless you've been livin' there for a couple centuries.」
			PRINTFORML 「But don't worry!」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grins.
			PRINTFORMW 「Just bring me along and I'll tell 'em you're my guest. Nobody's gonna risk insultin' an oomukade's honor.」

		CASE 13
			PRINTFORMW 「Hey, you got any of my Ability Cards?」
			PRINTFORMW 「I'm collectin' em. If you don't, you can buy somethin' from me.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I've got a bunch of semi-rares I'm willin' to sell. Picked 'em up tryin' to get a holographic Yamabiko's Mic.」

		CASE 14
			PRINTFORML 「Do you play the Moriya Lottery at all? If you don't, I'd recommend it.」
			PRINTFORMW 「It's a great way to get sports drinks. And those are great for when you work out.」
			PRINTFORMW 「'Course, you don't always get what you want. I've got more golden scrubbing brushes than I know what to do with...」

		CASE 15
			PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% sighs.
			PRINTFORMW 「Sometimes I wish Iizunamaru was more ambitious.」
			PRINTFORML 「%HES_SHES(140,1)% smart, %HES_SHES(140)% got great business sense, %HES_SHES(140)% a great Danmaku fighter...」
			PRINTFORMW 「%HES_SHES(140,1)% the perfect candidate to take over once Tenma retires.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Except %HE_SHE(140)% can't, 'cause %HES_SHES(140)% not a member of the Tenma clan. %HES_SHES(140,1)% already gone as high as %HE_SHE(140)% can go.」
			PRINTFORML 「And %HES_SHES(140)% just... okay with that!」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% throws up %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% hands in exasperation.
			PRINTFORMW 「I just don't get it. If I was %HIM_HER(140)%, I'd at least be frustrated about it... but %HE_SHE(140)% doesn't even care.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Maybe I'd understand if I was raised a tengu.」

		CASE 16
			PRINTFORML 「They call me "The %PRINT_MALE("Prince:Princess", [[百々世]])% Who Slays Dragon Kings", but ever since I came to Gensokyo, I ain't slain a single one.」
			PRINTFORMW 「They're surprisingly hard to find.」
			PRINTFORMW 「There's that Suiryuu the kappa worship and Tenryuu flyin' through space, but I've never run into 'em.」
			PRINTFORMW 「There's Ibaraki's pet dragon and Kicchou... but I'm not crazy enough to pick a fight with a Sage, or with the Hell Mafia.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Maybe I should take a trip to the Outside and see if they're easier to find out there.」

		CASE 17
			PRINTFORMW 「You ever been to the Moriya Shrine? Sometimes I go there to pray for good luck.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I don't usually ask the gods for favors, but I don't want 'em mad at me, either.」

		CASE 18
			PRINTFORMW 「Hoo boy... that Rika chick's got a few screws loose.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I was tryin' to see if I could buy explosives from her for cheap, and then she tried to rope me into attackin' the Hakurei Shrine!」
			PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% snorts.
			PRINTFORMW 「She told me I could eat Hakurei's Yin-Yang orb once we won.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I told her she was nuts, she called me a coward... and it ended with me runnin' outta her workshop chased by those Evil Eyes she makes.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I smashed 'em all up, of course. I just didn't want to start throwin' Danmaku around in a place full of gunpowder.」

		CASE 19
			PRINTFORMW 「One time, Tsukasa talked me into playing a round of mahjong at Komakusa's place.」
			PRINTFORMW 「"It'll be fun, %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]%-dono! Besides, you're so talented! I'm sure you'll do great!"」
			PRINTFORMDL %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% laughs bitterly.
			PRINTFORMW 「I ended up losing that week's paycheck.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I probably woulda done better if I coulda seen the tiles better.」
			PRINTFORMW 「My vision ain't great to begin with, and the place bein' super dark and full of smoke didn't help.」

		CASE 20
			PRINTFORMW 「Tsukasa's... interesting.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% thinks for a moment.
			PRINTFORMW 「%HE_SHE(139)%'s always super polite to Iizunamaru, Tenkyuu n' me. Callin' us "-dono" and all.」
			PRINTFORMW 「And %HE_SHE(139)% always gets great results. The whole Ability Card scheme'd never have gotten off the ground without %HIS_HER(139)% help.」
			PRINTFORMW 「But I dunno... I can't help but feel like it's all an act.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Maybe I'm just too cynical.」

		CASE 21
			PRINTFORMW 「Even though Iizunamaru's explained how the whole ability card market works, I still don't get it.」
			PRINTFORMW %BREAKENG(@"「Like... isn't it a bad idea to just let anybody drop the freakin' moon on people if they have Clownpiece's card? What if Kijin gets it?」")%
			PRINTFORMW 「But the one time I brought it up at a meeting, Tsukasa got mad and told me "just mine the gems, gem-miner!"」
			PRINTFORMDW Momoyo scowls.
			PRINTFORMW 「Jackass.」

		CASE 22
			PRINTFORMW 「What's Tenkyuu's deal?」
			PRINTFORMW %BREAKENG(@"「Every time I try to make small talk with her, she just goes on and on about market equilibriums and irrational exuberance and repugnancy costs and Pareto efficiency until I feel like my brain's gonna leak outta my ears.」")%
			PRINTFORML 「I know she's a market goddess, but c'mon, you don't gotta make that your whole personality!」
			PRINTFORMW 「I'm a miner, but I don't talk about mining all the time!」
			PRINTFORMW 「Iizunamaru's a great tengu, but she doesn't talk about tengu politics all the time!」
			PRINTFORML 「Tsukasa's a brown-noser, but she doesn't suck up to people all the ti-」
			PRINTFORMW 「Okay, that was a bad example. But you get what I'm sayin', right?」

		CASE 23
			PRINTFORMW 「You wanna know why I wear those ribbons, huh?」
			PRINTFORMDW Momoyo chuckles.
			PRINTFORMW 「They're power limiters. So if you beat me, don't get cocky. I'm only usin', uh... 40\% of my power!」
			PRINTFORMW 「Nah, I'm just kiddin'. It's an oomukade thing.」
			PRINTFORMW 「You wear strips of cloth, ribbons... anything that looks like a centipede's stripes.」
			PRINTFORML 「And the way you wear 'em tells other oomukade what clan and family you're from, plus some other stuff.」
			PRINTFORMW 「In my case, my ribbons show that I'm from the Himemushi clan of the Brokentooth tribe, I'm of noble birth...」
			PRINTFORMW 「And that I'm \@ TALENT:TARGET:恋人 ? taken # single\@.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% winks at you.
			PRINTFORMW 「And then the way we file our teeth shows our parentage.」
			PRINTFORMDW %HE_SHE([[百々世]],1)% grins.
			PRINTFORMW 「Just from that you can see I'm Momoyo, daughter of Hinawa, daughter of Yui.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Pretty cool, huh? It's how we make up for havin' crap memories.」

		CASE 24
			PRINTFORMW 「Iizunamaru's my oldest and best friend.」
			SIF TALENT:TARGET:恋人
				PRINTFORMW 「Well, other'n you, of course.」
			PRINTFORML 「%HE_SHE(140)% helped me get my bearings when I first came to Gensokyo, helped me get started doin' odd jobs...」
			PRINTFORMW 「I owe %HIM_HER(140)% a lot.」

		CASE 25
			PRINTFORML 「Y'know, the mountain didn't used to be this open to visitors.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Used to be that we kept to ourselves. Kinda like Sakata does.」
			PRINTFORML 「And if anyone trespassed, we all went after 'em. Tengu, kappa... everyone joined forces to throw 'em out.」
			PRINTFORMW 「We wanted to do our thing and let the rest of Gensokyo do theirs.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Hm? You wanna know why they didn't throw me out, too?」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% laughs.
			PRINTFORML 「%CALLNAME:MASTER%, I've been livin' here since before the Barrier went up.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I didn't come to Gensokyo. Gensokyo came to me!」
			PRINTFORMW 「Anyway, a couple decades back, Tenma decided to change things. Said it was bad for business.」
			PRINTFORMW 「And honestly... I like it better this way.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I mean, if we kept to the old ways, you and I probably never would'a met.」

		CASE 26
			PRINTFORMW 「Gensokyo's really changed a lot in the past couple decades, huh?」
			PRINTFORMW 「The Scarlet Devil Mansion showed up, people started travelin' between the Underworld and the surface...」
			PRINTFORMW 「The Moriya Shrine got moved to Youkai Mountain, Hijiri and Toyosatomimi came back...」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% laughs.
			PRINTFORMW 「I wonder who's gonna show up next?」

		CASE 27
			PRINTFORMW 「After Tenkyuu and Iizunamaru had their falling out, these black markets started poppin' up everywhere.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Apparently the yamawaro decided to take advantage of the market's instability to set up their own exchanges that they controlled.」
			PRINTFORML 「But Tenkyuu and Kawashiro worked with Kirisame to make them give up control of the markets and give 'em back to Tenkyuu. Or something.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% shrugs.
			PRINTFORMW 「Hey, I'm a miner, not an economist! Ask Tenkyuu if you want a better explanation.」

		CASE 28
			PRINTFORMW 「So you're an Outsider too, yeah?」
			PRINTFORMW 「You from Japan too? What's it like now?」
			PRINTFORMW 「I haven't been back since I came here... damn, a thousand years ago? Has it really been that long?」
			PRINTFORMW 「I hope those Fujiwara bastards aren't still runnin' things from behind the scenes...」

		CASE 29
			PRINTFORMW 「Y'know %CALLNAME:135%, the maneki-neko? %HES_SHES(135,1)% always tryin' to suck up to me.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Maybe it's cause centipedes are supposed to bring good luck to merchants? Or maybe %HE_SHE(135)% just thinks I'm cool.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Well, whatever the case, I try and buy cards from her when I can.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Gotta keep the economy stimulated! That's what Tenkyuu says.」

		CASE 30
			PRINTFORMW 「Iizunamaru lets us spend 20\% of our time workin' on side projects, as long as we present 'em to %HIM_HER(140)% and %HES_SHES(140)% okay with 'em.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Right now I'm plannin' out a tunnel between Youkai Mountain and the Scarlet Devil Mansion.」
			PRINTFORMW 「They employ loads of fairies that don't actually do anything, right? I bet they'd love to get their hands on some Ability Cards!」
			PRINTFORMDW Do fairies even have any money...?

		CASE 31
			PRINTFORMW 「Once a month, I get Ibuki to fill the Rainbow Dragon Cave with oxygen for a party.」
			PRINTFORMW 「All the strongest people in Gensokyo are there. We spar, trade fighting strategies... and of course, enjoy some quality sake.」
			PRINTFORMW 「You're welcome to come, if you wanna.」

		CASE 32
			PRINTFORMW 「So now that we're a couple... I should induct you into the Himemushi clan.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Let's see... we'll have to file your teeth so people know your mom and grandma's names...」
			PRINTFORMW 「You'll need to start wearing ribbons that indicate your clan and position in it...」
			PRINTFORMW 「Oh, and you'll have to kill and eat a dragon.」
			PRINTFORMDW What have you gotten yourself into...?

		CASE 33
			PRINTFORMW 「I keep gettin' distracted at my job now that we're datin'.」
			PRINTFORMW 「Every time I see a nice lookin' gem, I think to myself, "I wonder if it would look good on me? Would %CALLNAME:MASTER% like it?"」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% grimaces.
			PRINTFORMW 「Hope Iizunamaru doesn't get mad...」

		CASE 34
			PRINTFORMW 「A lot of my coworkers are jealous that I managed to snag a%COND_STR(" human", !IS_NONHUMAN(MASTER))% %PRINT_MALE("boy", MASTER)%friend.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% frowns.
			PRINTFORMW 「They better not try to steal you from me...」

		CASE 35
			PRINTFORMW 「So now that you're kinda sorta a member of the Himemushi clan... don't do anything to disgrace it, okay?」
			PRINTFORMW 「And if anyone insults you... just let me know.」
			PRINTFORMDW %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]% cracks %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% knuckles.
			PRINTFORMW 「I'll have a few choice words with 'em.」

		CASE 36
			PRINTFORMW 「I should probably re-learn how to do tea ceremonies.」
			PRINTFORMW 「I used to know, but with no other oomukade around, I never had a reason to do 'em and I forgot.」
			PRINTFORMW 「But a %PRINT_MALE("prince:princess", [[百々世]])% should know how to make tea for %HIS_HER([[百々世]])% lover.」

		CASE 37
			PRINTFORMW 「Hey, %CALLNAME:MASTER%... can you give me cooking lessons sometime?」
			PRINTFORMW 「It's traditional for a Himemushi to hunt and prepare their lover's dinner... but you guys don't eat raw meat.」

		CASE 38
			PRINTFORML 「Urgh... I friggin' hate winter...」
			PRINTFORMDW Momoyo shivers and hugs herself.
			PRINTFORMW 「No matter how much clothing I put on, or how many blankets I line my bed with, I still feel like I'm gonna freeze solid.」
			PRINTFORMW 「On top of that, I can never get a good night's sleep thanks to Tsukasa moaning her head off.」
			IF CFLAG:139:既成事実 & 合意_うふふ
				PRINTFORMDW Momoyo glares at you.
				PRINTFORMW 「And I know it's 'cause she's screwin' you all night long. Do you two have to be so damn loud?!」
				SIF CFLAG:[[百々世]]:既成事実 & 合意_うふふ
					PRINTFORMW 「At least let me join ya! We're sharin' you, ain't we?」
			ELSE
				PRINTFORML 「Who the hell does she think she's fooling?」
				PRINTFORMW 「We all know she ain't sharin' her bed with anyone.」
			ENDIF
			PRINTFORMDW She scowls.
			PRINTFORMW 「Makes me wish I could just hibernate until it warms back up...」

	ENDSELECT
ENDIF
RETURN 1
