						PRINTFORMW 「Oh, and you'll need about... \\10,000 yen. Trust me on this one.」
						CFLAG:[[百々世]]:K142EN_WORK_HELP_PERMISSION = 2
						RETURN 1
					ENDIF
					IF FIRSTTIME("YinYangExplanation")
						PRINTFORMDL 
						PRINTFORMDW When you empty the cart and bring it back to %CALLNAME:[[百々世]]%, you ask what those things were.
