;==================================================
;411,戦闘訓練
;TFLAG:194(3=夏の昼間 2=ヤバい天気 1=悪天候 0=屋内or通常天気
;==================================================
@M_KOJO_MESSAGE_COM_K142_411
CALL M_KOJO_MESSAGE_COM_K142_411_1
RETURN RESULT

@M_KOJO_MESSAGE_COM_K142_411_1
;-------------------------------------------------
;記入チェック（=0, 非表示、1, 表示）
LOCAL = 1
;-------------------------------------------------
IF LOCAL

	IF FIRSTTIME(SELECTCOM)
		PRINTFORMW 「Danmaku, huh?」
		PRINTFORMW 「Sure, we can spar. I respect weak people who try to get strong.」
		PRINTFORMW 「No offense meant.」
	ELSE
		IF ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力 <= 2
			SELECTCASE RAND:6
				CASE 0
					PRINTFORMW 「You don't wanna focus on just the area around you. You wanna focus on... mmm, anywhere that's within a couple seconds of you?」
					PRINTFORMW 「It's hard at first, with all the stuff flyin' around, but once you get it down, dodgin' becomes a lot easier.」
					PRINTFORMW 「You'll know where the safe spots are. and that's when you counterattack.」

				CASE 1
					PRINTFORMW 「Danmaku looks intimidatin' at first, but here's the thing... most of the bullets don't matter.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Only the stuff movin' toward you and the stuff movin' toward where you're gonna move does.」

				CASE 2
					PRINTFORMW 「"Bomb early, bomb often", that's my motto.」
					PRINTFORMW 「I know, I know, you wanna save your bombs for the really tough stuff.」
					PRINTFORMW 「But you'll waste more bombs if you get hit with bombs in stock than if you use 'em when you don't need 'em.」

				CASE 3
					PRINTFORMW 「Try not to stay too far away from the battlefield.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Not only is it way too easy to go too far and forfeit the match, it's also easy for your opponent to box you in.」

				CASE 4
					PRINTFORMW 「If you're havin' trouble, try takin' a break and watchin' other people duel.」
					PRINTFORMW 「You might learn some new tricks. Even seein' people screw up helps, 'cause you'll know what not to do in a similar situation.」

				CASE 5
					PRINTFORMW 「You wanna move slow most of the time.」
					PRINTFORMW 「It's temptin' to try and zip outta the way of everything, but you'll probably just crash into a bullet you didn't see.」

			ENDSELECT
		ELSEIF ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力 > 2 && ABL:MASTER:戦闘能力 < 5
			SELECTCASE RAND:6
				CASE 0
					PRINTFORMW 「Most people will aim their shots directly at you.」
					PRINTFORMW 「In the heat of battle, it can be tricky to try and fire at where you think the other guy's gonna be.」
					PRINTFORMW 「So if you only move a teeny bit, just enough to dodge whatever attacks coming toward you, you can dodge more stuff without gettin' boxed in.」

				CASE 1
					PRINTFORMW 「No matter what happens in a match, never give up.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Even if you screw up the first couple Spell Cards, who knows? Maybe somethin'll click and you'll dodge all their other ones.」
					PRINTFORMW 「It's happened to me before.」

				CASE 2
					PRINTFORMW 「Don't forget to keep comin' up with new Spell Cards!」
					PRINTFORMW 「Not only does it stop you from gettin' predictable, fightin' the same duels over and over ain't any fun.」

				CASE 3
					PRINTFORMW 「If you're doin' lots of duels with Ability Cards, do some experimentin'.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Lots of cards are useless on their own and crazy good when paired with others.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Just make sure to lay down some house rules if you're gonna do that. Some combos just ain't fair.」
					PRINTFORML 「Back before their cards got banned, everyone on Youkai Mountain was usin' Iizunamaru, Tsukasa, and Hijiri's cards.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Every fight was just "who runs outta bombs first"?」
					PRINTFORMDW Momoyo snorts.

				CASE 4
					PRINTFORMW 「If you keep losin', try tweakin' your scope and your regular shot.」
					PRINTFORMW 「You're gonna be usin' them for most of the fight, especially in no timeout duels.」

				CASE 5
					PRINTFORMW 「Sometimes bullet sizes can be deceivin'.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Y'ever dueled Knowledge? She fires those giant bullets in one of her cards, but only the inner parts actually hit ya. The rest of 'em pass right through.」
					PRINTFORMW 「On the other hand, there's Izayoi's knives. I've taken hits from 'em that I swear I shoulda dodged...」

			ENDSELECT
		ELSE
			SELECTCASE RAND:3
				CASE 0
					PRINTFORML 「At this point, you're good enough to start focusin' on makin' your Danmaku stylish.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Danmaku ain't just a sport, it's an art! Go nuts!」

				CASE 1
					PRINTFORML 「Y'ever tried Spellcards Only, Timeouts Only duels?」
					PRINTFORMW 「Really helped me improve my dodgin'. Still ain't good enough to throw in Sudden Death rules, but one day...」

				CASE 2
					PRINTFORMW 「Some of the most fun I've had in Danmaku matches have been with gimmick rules.」
					PRINTFORMW 「Me vs. Cirno where I had one Spell Card and she had four, fightin' both of the Tsukumo sisters at once, me vs. loads of fairies where I had to try and survive ten minutes without gettin' hit...」
					PRINTFORMW 「Heck, I heard Lapislazuli will do duels blindfolded.」

			ENDSELECT
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
RETURN 1
