		PRINTFORMDW Momoyo grins sheepishly at you.
		PRINTFORMW 「I dunno much about cooking...」
		PRINTFORMW 「I'm a Himemushi. Always figured my \@ IS_MALE(MASTER) ? husband # wife\@'d handle that.」
		PRINTFORMW 「But if you wanna teach me, I'm ready to learn. "Never back down from a challenge", that's my motto.」

